---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";

const title = "Privacy Policy â€“ Vitamin Brand Index";
const description = "How Vitamin Brand Index collects, uses, and protects information.";
const canonical = "https://vitaminbrandindex.com/privacy/";

const effectiveDate = "September 18, 2025";
---

<Base {title} {description} {canonical}>
  <main class="container stack-lg">
    <header class="page-header">
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>Privacy Policy Effective Date: {effectiveDate}</p>
    </header>

    <section class="stack">
      <p>Vitamin Brand Index ("we," "our," or "us") respects your privacy. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect information when you visit vitaminbrandindex.com.</p>

      <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Information You Provide:</strong> Newsletter signup (email address). Forms ("Request an Edit" and "Submit a Brand") may include name, email, role, brand name, comments, and any other details you choose to share.</li>
        <li><strong>Information Collected Automatically:</strong> Basic usage data such as pages visited, referral source, and device/browser information. We use Plausible Analytics for privacy-friendly, cookie-free analytics.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
      <p>Provide the directory, respond to form submissions, send newsletters to subscribers, and improve site performance. We do not sell or rent personal information.</p>

      <h2>Sharing of Information</h2>
      <p>We may share information with service providers (e.g., Formspree for forms, Beehiiv or another ESP for newsletters, Netlify for hosting) and as required by law. We do not share personal information for advertising or behavioral tracking.</p>

      <h2>Cookies and Tracking</h2>
      <p>We do not use cookies or cross-site trackers. Plausible does not use cookies or collect personally identifiable information.</p>

      <h2>Data Retention</h2>
      <p>Newsletter data is retained until you unsubscribe. Form submissions are retained as long as reasonably necessary to review and respond. You may request deletion at any time.</p>

      <h2>Your Rights</h2>
      <p>Depending on your location, you may have rights (e.g., GDPR/CCPA) to access, correct, delete, or withdraw consent. Contact: <a href="mailto:hello@vitaminbrandindex.com" class="link">hello@vitaminbrandindex.com</a>.</p>

      <h2>Security</h2>
      <p>We use reputable third-party processors and secure hosting. No method is 100% secure, but we take reasonable measures to reduce risk.</p>

      <h2>Children's Privacy</h2>
      <p>Not directed to individuals under 16; we do not knowingly collect information from children.</p>

      <h2>Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy. Updates will appear here with a new Effective Date.</p>

      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <p>Email: <a href="mailto:hello@vitaminbrandindex.com" class="link">hello@vitaminbrandindex.com</a></p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Base>
